{"tid":1875502,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"你地覺得文筆重要定故事性重要","createTime":"2020-02-11T22:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T12:26:01.000Z","uid":47268,"like":143,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3cb74b87a32ecd7dba9a39ba5c2ee54630479c","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:31:33.000Z","msg":"有唔少故文筆都相當唔錯但係內容唔夠吸引，比較悶<br />\n<br />\n而有啲故文筆都幾差，甚至成篇文都冇乜書面語，全部用口語寫，但又睇得明作者講乜，而故事內容幾風趣幽默，相當吸引<br />\n<br />\n你地會點簡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得故事性重要啲<br />\n因為我諗起爆漫有句「漫畫只要有趣就能夠連載」你畫幾靚都冇撚用，都唔吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩大把故文筆同故事性都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7094e1db4414e5daae62f7069c52d23c07c7728","tid":1875502,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:32:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2804b052a94962e3bada275680970c8bb0fb152","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:36:38.000Z","msg":"好耐以前高登有篇文叫「麥麥送死之乜乜柒柒」<br />\n<br />\n呢篇就好似我講咁<br />\n文筆同用詞都好普通<br />\n成篇文章都用口語黎寫<br />\n但故事性好撚吸引，人物性格都好撚正，仲要作者真係篤撚中曬我啲笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65176eec94adc5a35faae8570863ce96267623b","tid":1875502,"uid":46151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:45:19.000Z","msg":"其實要睇咩類型嘅故 好難一概而論<br />\n例如武俠故文筆更重要 鳩故就梗係故事性重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},{"pid":"a1344be8d8be046771c7f1a3a12cf70ac67b5ed7","tid":1875502,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d65176eec94adc5a35faae8570863ce96267623b","tid":1875502,"uid":46151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:45:19.000Z","msg":"其實要睇咩類型嘅故 好難一概而論<br />\n例如武俠故文筆更重要 鳩故就梗係故事性重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:53:30.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"dca874fd901d503313a2f2cd612c74e0942c82d1","tid":1875502,"uid":264837,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:54:11.000Z","msg":"用口語寫唔代表冇文筆<br />\n用字要簡單得嚟表達得好都係一種技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼你明佢講咩，唔會1999，又睇得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a15b402908c27e8dc9fd5f8462ffd05d5bf72a","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPddweq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPddweq.png&h=d681a7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲你會歸類成有文筆定冇文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331aac46ccf6b9d4bffed9fc3fa66e23789e4516","tid":1875502,"uid":189068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:44.000Z","msg":"我手寫我口就代表無文筆？<br />\n如果樓豬係咁嘅意思我就完全唔認同"},{"pid":"5fc6aa7a0fce1401ea3751605351a3d6e1ed14e0","tid":1875502,"uid":133929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:56:16.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"322091d9821033a0a2061917115b155a7aca0b8a","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"331aac46ccf6b9d4bffed9fc3fa66e23789e4516","tid":1875502,"uid":189068,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:44.000Z","msg":"我手寫我口就代表無文筆？<br />\n如果樓豬係咁嘅意思我就完全唔認同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"我講既冇文筆應該係比「我迷失在一場情遊戲」好少少既程度<br />\n<br />\n你點都睇得明想寫啲咩<br />\n但只係比小學雞既作文程度好少少"},{"pid":"8c2d85f73d071ced1426a48506e7b4d6358997a9","tid":1875502,"uid":243854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:59:28.000Z","msg":"唔好扭曲人哋意思<br />\n事實上有幾多人平時講嘢會有&ldquo;文筆&rdquo;？<br />\n如果要廣東話又文筆好，我諗真係要熟讀文言文古詞。"},{"pid":"7737b565a3b8b5d65e87dd3e2415ffa5cb136c47","tid":1875502,"uid":42927,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T23:14:38.000Z","msg":"寫故寫到文縐縐撚會有人睇咩，你估香港人個個睇開古典文學㗎咩？<br />\n<br />\n傳統白話文小說都唔係個個鍾意睇啦，依家時下啲香港人都係睇開白話文加口語入文，文筆好壞都冇人會在意。<br />\n<br />\n除非係走傳統文學路線，先至需要着重文筆，否則你睇下依家大部分嘅流行小說作家寫嘅嘢，其實都冇咩文筆可言。<br />\n<br />\n好似日本人寫啲小說都係咁，成日寫到1999，寫到好累贅，但係佢哋通常靠sell創意同故事性，所以寫嘅嘢都可以好多人鍾意睇。"},{"pid":"e5b16994e2e4f06c8f9b56ea4d900f3520b74a1d","tid":1875502,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T00:50:29.000Z","msg":"梗係故事性<br />\n睇到訓著嘅話我比你文筆識飛天都無用"},{"pid":"f8fd42f60c41ad51805544c805a5ee43494d78e7","tid":1875502,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:27:25.000Z","msg":"吸引嚟講一定係故事性重要啲<br />\n舉個例子就好似啲文學作品咁 啲人嗰嗰文筆好到曉飛 但都係會睇到瞓覺<br />\n故事性好嘅故文筆唔洗太好 通順睇得明就得 門檻自然低啲都易入口啲"},{"pid":"48100ca40c62f595e2386153dae553caf0c21fda","tid":1875502,"uid":130205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:35:11.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"89101bccbd37009efcf44802875eeefc89348faa","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:07:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef3ff344ea9513927816e24d80f0845e56f94c77","tid":1875502,"uid":255940,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"93a15b402908c27e8dc9fd5f8462ffd05d5bf72a","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPddweq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPddweq.png&h=d681a7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲你會歸類成有文筆定冇文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"我會當有文筆<br />\n我覺得口語同書面語都可以有文筆高低之分 口語只係現代化<br />\n<br />\n高低分別在於文句通唔通順 鋪排手法 同描述得夠唔夠仔細同深入<br />\n<br />\n你引果篇都有環境有對話 對話用字上又表達到角色特質 對應既語氣都比番出黎<br />\n環境表達到周圍既野 但氣氛差d<br />\n我會咁理解文筆"},{"pid":"c9a4d32ada2b308b917cf15f8b2ccc5faab659bf","tid":1875502,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"諗起32歲毒男的自白"},{"pid":"ec1b9a360b45145fa5eb8299cd74f0deb1b375e6","tid":1875502,"uid":51088,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"why not both？<br />\n睇個人口味，我自己就追求有基本文筆先得。<br />\n如果文筆真係差到１９９９，我會索性唔睇。<br />\n同埋要視乎你書齡同嗰時嘅心情，一般嚟講會愈食愈奄尖。<br />\n人嘅時間就有限嘅，文筆係可以一兩段內睇得到作者個人功架嘅因素，可以慳番啲時間做scanning。"},{"pid":"1a82ce9cb334a513e7e13c147265408207f76c55","tid":1875502,"uid":281401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:48:35.000Z","msg":"一定係故事性<br />\n<br />\n睇過啲故事, 文字好靚, 但故事性欠奉, 講極都係廢話, 詞藻同手法幾華麗都係廢話。"},{"pid":"bcafe2dcaae06eb52444641606fc1482007e8df4","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a15b402908c27e8dc9fd5f8462ffd05d5bf72a","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPddweq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPddweq.png&h=d681a7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲你會歸類成有文筆定冇文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"呢篇嘢轉晒做書面語就係有文筆？<br />\n有無文筆係睇你點寫點鋪排<br />\n唔關你用咩語言事"},{"pid":"ba425126d63ff13f004d1135e71e9f920ba77fdb","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2d85f73d071ced1426a48506e7b4d6358997a9","tid":1875502,"uid":243854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:59:28.000Z","msg":"唔好扭曲人哋意思<br />\n事實上有幾多人平時講嘢會有&ldquo;文筆&rdquo;？<br />\n如果要廣東話又文筆好，我諗真係要熟讀文言文古詞。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"呢個講法同樣適用於普通話書面語<br />\n廣東話保留更加多文言文用字同文法<br />\n係你睇唔順眼覺得書面語先叫有文筆"},{"pid":"2e538a5a118fd7b31f4202aa3e6f070cab0e9f26","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:04:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc457c981672aa4bc1dbf532a4fade6054a0d139","tid":1875502,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1344be8d8be046771c7f1a3a12cf70ac67b5ed7","tid":1875502,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d65176eec94adc5a35faae8570863ce96267623b","tid":1875502,"uid":46151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-1