性重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T19:03:47.000Z","msg":"近排個&lt;我有口罩，你有西嗎&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33c449c6ff25bc1b6756e839d94291f6f98bcb7","tid":1875502,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"故事係一種藝術<br />\n文筆又係另一種藝術"},{"pid":"4f0b4502d930203a8638ed297cc5872ae8377701","tid":1875502,"uid":243854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba425126d63ff13f004d1135e71e9f920ba77fdb","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c2d85f73d071ced1426a48506e7b4d6358997a9","tid":1875502,"uid":243854,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:59:28.000Z","msg":"唔好扭曲人哋意思<br />\n事實上有幾多人平時講嘢會有&ldquo;文筆&rdquo;？<br />\n如果要廣東話又文筆好，我諗真係要熟讀文言文古詞。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"呢個講法同樣適用於普通話書面語<br />\n廣東話保留更加多文言文用字同文法<br />\n係你睇唔順眼覺得書面語先叫有文筆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T19:27:06.000Z","msg":"廣東話保留更加多文言文用字同文法<br />\n呢句咪答返你自己囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我咪講咗學好文言文廣東話落筆更有文筆<br />\nBTW其實書面語唔代表=普通話口語"},{"pid":"8cf0deddd9c4181b8fa3438b44065a074c6991bf","tid":1875502,"uid":136537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2804b052a94962e3bada275680970c8bb0fb152","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:36:38.000Z","msg":"好耐以前高登有篇文叫「麥麥送死之乜乜柒柒」<br />\n<br />\n呢篇就好似我講咁<br />\n文筆同用詞都好普通<br />\n成篇文章都用口語黎寫<br />\n但故事性好撚吸引，人物性格都好撚正，仲要作者真係篤撚中曬我啲笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T19:37:39.000Z","msg":"我都有追過！！<br />\n大結局果日 作者仲搞左麥當勞gathering<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講起好想追番！"},{"pid":"36d6d1c14f18316281354df47a4dd10a5ffa0327","tid":1875502,"uid":187676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T19:51:06.000Z","msg":"文筆只係工具，用黎正確傳達你個故事既中心思想<br />\n你既文章有冇思想同靈魂先係最重要"},{"pid":"a2ffb27f22e64ab579b3d0da15c182025890cd5f","tid":1875502,"uid":344231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a15b402908c27e8dc9fd5f8462ffd05d5bf72a","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPddweq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPddweq.png&h=d681a7cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲你會歸類成有文筆定冇文筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T06:30:11.000Z","msg":"咩名？想睇"},{"pid":"e9ab410e6a3a2cee36ac6f8f2a17924925414b14","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ffb27f22e64ab579b3d0da15c182025890cd5f","tid":1875502,"uid":344231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93a15b402908c27e8dc9fd5f8462ffd05d5bf72a","tid":1875502,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b287dfb95897633a9cc6a16c849c2bf3e6490097","tid":1875502,"uid":206594,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:51:51.000Z","msg":"點撚解你覺得口語就係無文筆？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPddweq.png\"