ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"諗起無限恐怖<br />\n<br />\n文筆爛到乜咁，但故事世界觀真係無敵"},{"pid":"a509633625711d3b2428f9f24fcba6618df1bf83","tid":1875502,"uid":207957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"諗返起以前 西西西西西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf6eb95be70d1dac4c29122490d489e195e461a","tid":1875502,"uid":246348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3d0a731a3f60ac5a272cce4d59b4b7707d0f8c4","tid":1875502,"uid":169133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"諗起無限恐怖<br />\n<br />\n文筆爛到乜咁，但故事世界觀真係無敵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可惜keep唔到<br />\n睇完無限恐怖當成個故事完哂，之後果d無限xx全部掀兩頁放棄"},{"pid":"1293ff3d2a27b5ba7b90f817e7aa7c33b50a23b7","tid":1875502,"uid":209738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"故事性，因為文筆再差都可以攞個劇本去畫漫畫丶拍電影丶做遊戲或者錄廣播劇。"},{"pid":"e488c25e3a08c89b4a39f28bd4bea12dd183cc6c","tid":1875502,"uid":13818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"一拳超人原作就係答案"},{"pid":"3a903c3bc6758a20808caebf4da4224c069bee1e","tid":1875502,"uid":169133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caf6eb95be70d1dac4c29122490d489e195e461a","tid":1875502,"uid":246348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3d0a731a3f60ac5a272cce4d59b4b7707d0f8c4","tid":1875502,"uid":169133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"諗起無限恐怖<br />\n<br />\n文筆爛到乜咁，但故事世界觀真係無敵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可惜keep唔到<br />\n睇完無限恐怖當成個故事完哂，之後果d無限xx全部掀兩頁放棄"},"citedBy":0,"